security: Revealing that the CIA is actively checking with Nosnko regarding Wallenberg and information on PD DIPPERS would expose intelligence-gathering methods, sources, and ongoing investigations, potentially compromising future operations. Quoting directly: "WE HAVE BEGUN CHECKING WITH NOSENKO. [PD DIPPERS 19 AND 20. AND LADLE RE WALLENBERG AND WILL CABLE OR TELEPOUCH RESULTS AS RECEIVED. WE EXPECT TO BE FINISHED BY MID-NOVEMBER-V"
summary: An outgoing message indicates that checks are being conducted with Nosenko regarding Wallenberg and PD DIPPERS, with results expected by mid-November.
summary_one_paragraph: This SECRET outgoing message, dated 232013Z, details that the CIA is actively checking with Nosenko on matters related to Wallenberg and PD DIPPERS 19 and 20, with a projected completion date around mid-November. The message, disseminated by multiple units, references file 201-5935 and is cross-filed for 201-099788. It instructs not to destroy the document.
title: UNINTEL, CKTOP TIBLOCK V
